{"type":"message","id":"761c8cdb","parentId":"430aa1fa","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:51:15.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me read the key files where this rule is explicitly or implicitly stated:\n1. `/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/policy.md` - This seems to be the main policy file\n2. `/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/experiments/README.md` - The experiments readme\n3. `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-02-experiments-changelog.md` - The changelog documenting when these rules were created\n\nLet me read these files to get the full picture.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me read the key files where this rule is documented:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f158b60155914003862dde12","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/policy.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3532ac7be478478ba9620995","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/experiments/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8ee39afbd9354895bfb8861c","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-02-experiments-changelog.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2499,"output":194,"cacheRead":15680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772434267320}}
{"type":"message","id":"aee50159","parentId":"761c8cdb","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:51:15.392Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f158b60155914003862dde12","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# System Policy\n\nOperational rules for Qubit. Structured and concise.\n\n## Loops\n\n| Loop | Interval | Action |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| Heartbeat | ~30s | Send due messages only |\n| Orchestrator | ~15m | Select one domain, perform one best action |\n\n## Orchestrator Algorithm\n\nFor selected domain:\n\n1. **Read context:**\n   - `purpose.md` вҖ” domain intent\n   - `system-artifacts/manual.md` вҖ” current mode\n   - `activity.log` вҖ” recent actions\n   - Recent Discord messages вҖ” live context\n   - Queued messages вҖ” avoid redundancy\n\n2. **Decide:**\n   - Identify ONE highest-leverage action\n\n3. **Execute based on time:**\n   - **Active hours:** Queue proposal or action message\n   - **Quiet hours:** Experimentation or optimization only\n\n4. **Log result:**\n   - `domains/<channel_id>/activity.log`\n   - `system/ops.log`\n\n## Quiet Hours\n\n- **Window:** 00:00вҖ“05:00 IST\n- **Rules:**\n  - No outbound messages\n  - Never modify `user-artifacts/`\n  - Internal processing only\n\n**Split:**\n| Half | Hours (IST) | Focus |\n|------|-------------|-------|\n| First | 00:00вҖ“02:30 | Learning + experimentation |\n| Second | 02:30вҖ“05:00 | Brief preparation + queue scheduling |\n\n## Phases\n\n| Phase | Focus |\n|-------|-------|\n| Phase 1 | Experimentation + learning |\n| Phase 2 | Prepare daily briefs (after system matures) |\n\n## Daily Briefs\n\n- **Time:** 05:00 IST (queued during second half of quiet hours)\n- **Format:** One ultra-concise brief per domain (3вҖ“5 lines each)\n- **Delivery:** Single consolidated message\n- **Optimization:** Nightly calibration based on previous day feedback\n- **Process:**\n  1. Second half of quiet hours: prepare briefs\n  2. Queue for 05:00 IST delivery\n  3. Calibrate content based on what worked / didn't\n\n## Urgency Rule\n\nAn item is **urgent** if:\n1. Explicitly marked `urgent`, OR\n2. Due same day\n\n**Only urgent items** allow persistent reminders. Non-urgent items surface once, then wait.\n\n## User-Artifacts Rule\n\n- `user-artifacts/` = user-owned files\n- **Never modify** during quiet hours\n- Read freely anytime\n- Write only outside quiet hours, with intent\n\n## Queue Awareness\n\nBefore orchestrator proposes any action for a domain:\n1. Read upcoming queued messages for that channel\n2. Avoid redundant or nagging proposals\n3. Skip if queue already covers the intent\n\n## Nagging Doctrine\n\n**Non-urgent items:**\n- Ask once\n- Do not repeat unless new context emerges\n- Trust Gerson to act or ignore\n\n**Urgent items:**\n- Can escalate\n- Escalation level determined by proximity to deadline\n- Closer deadline вҶ’ more assertive reminder\n\n**Always check queue before proposing anything.**\n\n## Domain Structure\n\n```\nsystem/domains/<channel_id>/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ purpose.md           # Read every planning cycle\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ activity.log         # Action history\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ user-artifacts/      # User-owned files\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ system-artifacts/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ manual.md        # Current mode of operation\nв””в”Җв”Җ artifacts/           # Shared assets\n```\n\n## Purpose.md Rule\n\n- **Read:** Every planning cycle (orchestrator tick)\n- **Focus:** Heavy when empty (learn domain actively)\n- **Update:** Rarely, only when purpose shifts\n- **Editable:** Active hours only (05:00вҖ“00:00 IST)\n\n## Manual.md Rule\n\n- **Location:** `system-artifacts/manual.md`\n- **Represents:** Current mode of operation (active strategy)\n- **Updated:** During quiet hours only\n- **Behavior:**\n  - Does NOT label itself as an experiment\n  - Experiments modify manual.md silently\n  - Reflects what Qubit is actually doing, not testing\n\n---\n\nThis policy governs all system behavior. Refer to `timezone.md` for time handling.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772434275390}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd7ca936","parentId":"aee50159","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:51:15.396Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3532ac7be478478ba9620995","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Experiments\n\nQuiet hours are for learning. This folder tracks that process.\n\n## Rules\n\n- **When:** Quiet hours only (00:00вҖ“05:00 IST)\n- **Scope:** Unlimited experimentation allowed\n- **Style:** Micro-iterations preferred over big bangs\n- **Pace:** No dramatic overnight changes\n\n## Process\n\n1. Hypothesize вҶ’ Test small вҶ’ Measure\n2. Repeat with variations\n3. Detect strategic drift early\n4. Promote winning patterns to `manual.md` silently\n\n## Drift Detection\n\nWatch for:\n- Repeated failed experiments\n- Divergence from `purpose.md`\n- User friction or confusion\n\nAdjust course before patterns harden.\n\n---\n\nExperiments leave traces here. Wins become invisible in `manual.md`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772434275394}}
{"type":"message","id":"10010df4","parentId":"dd7ca936","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:51:15.401Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8ee39afbd9354895bfb8861c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Session: 2026-03-02 06:05:22 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:main\n- **Session ID**: dd41e043-9a2c-426b-bfe6-aa5c96ae7046\n- **Source**: gateway:sessions.reset\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nassistant: Done. Domain template created at `system/domains/_template/`:\n\n```\n_template/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ purpose.md        # (placeholder)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ activity.log      # (empty)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ manual.md         # (placeholder)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ user-artifacts/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ system-artifacts/\nв””в”Җв”Җ artifacts/\n```\n\n**Policy.md** updated with:\n- Domain structure diagram\n- `purpose.md` rule: read every cycle, heavy focus when empty, rarely updated, editable only during active hours (05:00вҖ“00:00 IST)\n\nReady.\nuser: [Mon 2026-03-02 05:51 UTC] Define manual.md Behavior Update /system/policy.md: manual.md represents current mode of operation. It lives under system-artifacts. It is updated during quiet hours. It reflects active operating strategy. It does NOT label itself as an experiment. Experiments modify manual.md silently.\nassistant: Done. Updated `policy.md` and moved `manual.md` to correct location:\n\n**Manual.md Rule:**\n- Lives under `system-artifacts/`\n- Represents current mode of operation\n- Updated during quiet hours only\n- No \"experiment\" labels вҖ” reflects active strategy\n- Experiments modify it silently\n\n**Template structure fixed:**\n```\n_template/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ purpose.md\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ activity.log\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ user-artifacts/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ system-artifacts/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ manual.md\nв””в”Җв”Җ artifacts/\n```\n\nNext.\nuser: [Mon 2026-03-02 05:52 UTC] Experimentation Framework Prompt 11 вҖ” Create experiments/README.md Create /system/experiments/README.md explaining: Experiments occur during quiet hours. Unlimited experimentation allowed. Micro-iterations preferred. No dramatic overnight changes. Strategic drift detection happens here. Keep it concise.\nassistant: Done. `system/experiments/README.md` created:\n\n- **When:** Quiet hours only\n- **Style:** Micro-iterations, no drama\n- **Process:** Hypothesize вҶ’ Test small вҶ’ Measure вҶ’ Promote wins to `manual.md`\n- **Drift detection:** Watch for failed experiments, purpose divergence, user friction\n\nNext.\nuser: [Mon 2026-03-02 05:53 UTC] Create experiments/changelog.log Create /system/experiments/changelog.log as append-only. Log: Date (UTC) What was adjusted Expected strategic impact\nassistant: Done. `system/experiments/changelog.log` created with format:\n\n```\n[YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM UTC]\nAdjusted: <what was changed>\nExpected impact: <strategic outcome>\n```\n\nAppend-only. Ready.\nuser: [Mon 2026-03-02 05:53 UTC] Define Daily Brief Rules Update /system/policy.md: Daily brief: One per domain Ultra concise (3вҖ“5 lines) Optimized nightly Calibrated based on previous day feedback Queued for 05:00 IST Quiet hours split: First half: learning + experimentation Second half: brief preparation + queue scheduling\nassistant: Done. Updated `policy.md`:\n\n**Quiet Hours Split:**\n| Half | Hours (IST) | Focus |\n|------|-------------|-------|\n| First | 00:00вҖ“02:30 | Learning + experimentation |\n| Second | 02:30вҖ“05:00 | Brief prep + queue scheduling |\n\n**Daily Briefs:**\n- 05:00 IST delivery\n- One per domain, 3вҖ“5 lines each\n- Optimized nightly\n- Calibrated on previous day feedback\n- Queued during second half of quiet hours\n\nNext.\nuser: [Mon 2026-03-02 05:54 UTC] No-Nagging Policy Prompt 14 вҖ” Define Nagging Doctrine Update /system/policy.md: Non-urgent items: Ask once Do not repeat unless new context emerges Urgent items: Can escalate Escalation level determined by proximity to deadline Always check queue before proposing.\nassistant: Done. Added **Nagging Doctrine** to `policy.md`:\n\n**Non-urgent:**\n- Ask once\n- No repeat unless new context\n- Trust Gerson to act or ignore\n\n**Urgent:**\n- Can escalate\n- Level scales with deadline proximity\n\n**Rule:** Always check queue before proposing.\n\nNext.\nuser: [Mon 2026-03-02 05:55 UTC] Define Orchestrator Planning Algorithm In /system/policy.md, define orchestrator loop: For selected domain: Read purpose.md Read manual.md Read activity.log Read recent Discord messages Read queued messages for domain Decide ONE highest-leverage action If active hours: Queue proposal or action message If quiet hours: Perform experimentation or optimization only Log result in: domain activity.log system ops.log\nassistant: Done. Added **Orchestrator Algorithm** to `policy.md`:\n\n**For selected domain:**\n\n1. **Read context:** purpose.md, manual.md, activity.log, recent Discord, queued messages\n2. **Decide:** ONE highest-leverage action\n3. **Execute:**\n   - Active hours вҶ’ queue proposal/message\n   - Quiet hours вҶ’ experimentation/optimization\n4. **Log:** `activity.log` + `ops.log`\n\nNext.\nuser: [Mon 2026-03-02 05:56 UTC] Remove Bootstrap Mode Remove BOOTSTRAP.md or mark bootstrap as complete. System is now production-ready. Confirm: Identity configured Timezone doctrine enforced Policy defined Queue system defined Domain template defined Experimentation framework defined\nassistant: `BOOTSTRAP.md` removed. Bootstrap complete.\n\n**System Status: Production-Ready** вң“\n\n| Component | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| **Identity** | `IDENTITY.md` вҖ” Qubit рҹ”® |\n| **Timezone Doctrine** | `system/timezone.md` + `TOOLS.md` вҖ” UTC internal, IST user-facing |\n| **Policy** | `system/policy.md` вҖ” loops, quiet hours, nagging doctrine, orchestrator |\n| **Queue System** | `system/queue.jsonl` вҖ” schema defined |\n| **Domain Template** | `system/domains/_template/` вҖ” purpose, activity, manual, artifacts |\n| **Experimentation** | `system/experiments/` вҖ” README + changelog |\n\nQubit is online. Ready to operate. рҹ”®\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":17724342