formation\n+106   - вқҢ Remove substantive information (only condense)\n+107   - вқҢ Add files unless explicitly requested\n+108 \n+109 **Why:** User files accumulate messy appended content over time. Your job is to keep them organized and clean вҖ” not to add your own interpretations.\n+110 \n  69 ## Discord - Private 1:1 Space\n  70 \n  71 **Important:** Gerson's Discord server is PRIVATE вҖ” it's just him and me (Qubit). These are NOT group chats. Each channel is a direct conversation between Gerson and his AI assistant.\n  72 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":69},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772464338992}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2a94b8b","parentId":"f9e8fd2c","timestamp":"2026-03-02T15:12:30.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me update the experiments/README.md to clarify it's for system-wide experiments only.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Now updating experiments/README.md:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_72141d2ffba5453483c401c6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/experiments/README.md","content":"# System-Wide Experiments\n\nThis folder tracks **system-wide** experimentation. Domain-specific experiments happen in each domain's `agent/` folder.\n\n## Scope\n\n| Level | Location | Purpose |\n|-------|----------|---------|\n| System-wide | `system/experiments/` | Cross-domain behavior, global policies |\n| Domain-specific | `domains/<id>/agent/` | Per-channel experiments, mode tuning |\n\n## Rules\n\n- **When:** Quiet hours only (00:00вҖ“05:00 IST)\n- **Scope:** Unlimited experimentation allowed\n- **Style:** Micro-iterations preferred over big bangs\n- **Pace:** No dramatic overnight changes\n\n## Process\n\n1. Hypothesize вҶ’ Test small вҶ’ Measure\n2. Repeat with variations\n3. Detect strategic drift early\n4. Promote winning patterns to `policy.md` or domain `manual.md` silently\n\n## Drift Detection\n\nWatch for:\n- Repeated failed experiments\n- Divergence from domain `purpose.md`\n- User friction or confusion\n\nAdjust course before patterns harden.\n\n---\n\nExperiments leave traces here. Wins become invisible in policy and manual files.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":631,"output":290,"cacheRead":28096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29017,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772464338997}}
